        <body>
            <div type="edition" subtype="transliteration-primary" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="xpu-Latn" resp="#JP" source="#autopsy">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1" style="text-direction:r-to-l"/>qbr <persName type="attested"><name>ḥ<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/>ʿṣ</name>
                    <lb n="2" style="text-direction:r-to-l"/>bn <persName type="attested"><name>ʿzry</name></persName></persName>
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp><app><note>Text of De Simone from autopys</note></app></listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#RDS">
                <p>Tomb of ḥ[...]ʿṣ, son of ʿzry</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="#RDS">
                <p>Tomba di ḥ[...]ʿṣ, figlio di ʿzry</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" resp="#RDS" xml:lang="en">
                <p>The name of the deceased cannot be reconstructed. ʿ<foreign xml:lang="xpu-Latn">zry</foreign> is a hypocoristic Phoenician personal name with suffix -y from the root <foreign xml:lang="xpu-Latn">ʿzr</foreign> "to help". </p>
            </div>
